  "mainOuterHtml": "<main id=\"MainContent\" class=\"content-for-layout focus-none\" role=\"main\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n      <div id=\"shopify-section-template--27935319752870__article_nBjnMW\" class=\"shopify-section\"><style data-shopify=\"\">\n  .article_content__wrpr {\n    padding-top: calc(16px / 2);\n    padding-bottom: calc(16px / 2);\n  }\n  .article__hero-banner, .article__hero-banner img {\n    border-radius: 10px;\n  }\n  .section-template--27935319752870__article_nBjnMW-padding {\n    padding-top:  calc(16px / 2);\n    margin-left: 12px;\n    margin-right: 12px;\n    padding-bottom: calc(16px / 2);\n  }\n  @media screen and (min-width: 787px) {\n    .article_content__wrpr {\n      padding-top: 16px;\n      padding-bottom: 16px;\n    }\n    .section-template--27935319752870__article_nBjnMW-padding {\n      padding-top: 16px;\n      padding-bottom: 16px;\n    }\n  }\n</style>\n\n<link href=\"//dynamic-preview.myshopify.com/cdn/shop/t/18/assets/main-article.css?v=172269203489927186851771645050\" rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" media=\"all\">\n\n<div class=\"main-article__wrpr section-template--27935319752870__article_nBjnMW-padding color-scheme-1\">\n  <div class=\"article__hero-banner narrow-width\">\n    \n      <img src=\"//dynamic-preview.myshopify.com/cdn/shop/articles/img_5.png?v=1770809328&amp;width=800\" alt=\"Your Daily Glow Guide\" srcset=\"//dynamic-preview.myshopify.com/cdn/shop/articles/img_5.png?v=1770809328&amp;width=352 352w, //dynamic-preview.myshopify.com/cdn/shop/articles/img_5.png?v=1770809328&amp;width=800 800w\" width=\"800\" height=\"958\" loading=\"lazy\">\n    \n  </div>\n  <div class=\"narrow-width\">\n    <div class=\"article_content__wrpr\">\n      \n        \n            \n            <span class=\"date\">07 Jan 2026</span>\n\n          \n      \n        \n            \n\n          \n      \n        \n            <span class=\"article_blog_title\">Blog</span>\n\n          \n      \n        \n            <div class=\"article__content\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;margin-top: 10px;\">\n              <h1 class=\"h3\">Your Daily Glow Guide</h1>\n            </div>\n\n          \n      \n        \n            <div class=\"article__content\">\n              <h2>Morning: Wake Up Your Radiance</h2>\n\n<p>Start your day by gently cleansing away overnight oils and impurities. Follow with a vitamin C serum to brighten and protect against environmental stressors. Don't forget a lightweight moisturizer with SPF—sun protection is the single most important step for maintaining youthful, glowing skin.</p>\n\n<h2>Midday: Refresh and Rehydrate</h2>\n\n<p>Keep a facial mist at your desk or in your bag for a quick hydration boost throughout the day. If your skin feels dry, pat in a few drops of facial oil or a hydrating essence. Remember to drink plenty of water—hydration from within shows on your skin.</p>\n\n<h2>Evening: Repair and Renew</h2>\n\n<p>Your nighttime routine is when the magic happens. Double cleanse to remove makeup, sunscreen, and the day's buildup. Apply targeted treatments like retinol or peptide serums, then seal everything in with a nourishing night cream. This is when your skin does its repair work, so give it the nutrients it needs.</p>\n\n<h2>Weekly Rituals</h2>\n\n<p>Set aside time 2-3 times a week for deeper treatments. Exfoliate gently to remove dead skin cells and reveal fresh, glowing skin underneath. Follow with a hydrating or clarifying mask based on your skin's needs. These extra steps make a noticeable difference in your skin's texture and radiance.</p>\n\n<h2>Lifestyle Tips for Lasting Glow</h2>\n\n<p>Great skin isn't just about products. Get enough sleep, manage stress through meditation or exercise, eat a balanced diet rich in antioxidants, and stay hydrated. Your skin reflects your overall wellness, so take care of your whole self.</p>\n\n<h2>Listen to Your Skin</h2>\n\n<p>Remember, your skin's needs change with the seasons, your hormones, and your lifestyle. Pay attention to what it's telling you and adjust your routine accordingly. Consistency is key, but flexibility is important too.</p>\n\n<p>Ready to glow? Start with these simple steps and watch your skin transform.</p>\n            </div>\n        \n      \n\n      <hr class=\"hr\">\n\n      <div class=\"article_page__social-icons align_ment--start\">\n        <button class=\"button article_page__social-share\" onclick=\"sharePage()\">\n          <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 48 48\" width=\"144px\" height=\"144px\">\n            <path d=\"M 36.5 5 A 6.5 6.5 0 0 0 30.236328 13.207031 L 30.121094 13.263672 L 16.738281 19.953125 L 16.623047 20.009766 A 6.5 6.5 0 0 0 11.5 17.5 A 6.5 6.5 0 0 0 11.5 30.5 A 6.5 6.5 0 0 0 16.626953 27.990234 L 16.738281 28.046875 L 30.121094 34.736328 L 30.230469 34.791016 A 6.5 6.5 0 0 0 36.5 43 A 6.5 6.5 0 0 0 36.5 30 A 6.5 6.5 0 0 0 31.671875 32.158203 L 31.460938 32.052734 L 18.080078 25.363281 L 17.871094 25.259766 A 6.5 6.5 0 0 0 17.869141 22.742188 L 18.080078 22.636719 L 31.460938 15.947266 L 31.666016 15.84375 A 6.5 6.5 0 0 0 36.5 18 A 6.5 6.5 0 0 0 36.5 5 z\"></path>\n          </svg>\n          Share\n        </button>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n      <div class=\"article_comments_section color-scheme-3\">\n        <div class=\"page-width\">\n          \n            \n\n            <div class=\"article_comment_form\">\n              <form method=\"post\" action=\"/blogs/news/your-daily-glow-guide/comments#comment_form\" id=\"comment_form\" accept-charset=\"UTF-8\" class=\"comment-form\"><input type=\"hidden\" name=\"form_type\" value=\"new_comment\" style=\"\"><input type=\"hidden\" name=\"utf8\" value=\"✓\" style=\"\">\n                <h3 class=\"h3\">Leave a comment</h3>\n\n                \n\n                <div class=\"author_email_text\">\n                  <input type=\"text\" name=\"comment[author]\" id=\"author\" value=\"\" placeholder=\"Full name *\" required=\"\" style=\"\">\n